# persister itself reads NO environment variables — it has no secrets of its own.
#
# Google Drive credentials are NOT env vars: they live as files in .secrets/ —
#   .secrets/client_secret.json   (OAuth client; chmod 600)
#   .secrets/token.json           (cached OAuth token, written on first auth; chmod 600)
#   .secrets/drive_state.json     (remembered Drive file_ids; chmod 600)
#
# This file exists only to satisfy the `!.env.example` gitignore convention shared
# across the sibling projects. Copy to `.env` only if a downstream caller needs one.
